0:

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: purdue dining
des:
Ask Purdue Dining Menu skill lets you find out what food is offered at one of Purdue's dining courts. You can ask for the menu at one location, and it will recite the food items at closest mealtime. 
The skill requires no account and does not use any personal information.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
